body:
Currently tristana is a grab bag of parts from other hyper carriers(who she mostly predates) having weaker parts from each of their kits

She has less range than {{champion:96}} {{champion:29}} {{champion:222}} when they have their steriods up, her only advantage is that her&#039;s is constant and with no draw back, but it is still less advantagous than what these guys have 

She has a reset that is  worst than jinx&#039;s by far, and even arguably worst than twitch&#039;s because he also gets a reset on his attackspeed steriod

She doesn&#039;t have as much aoe as jinx, or twitch and her wave clear is way worst than {{champion:222}} 

her dps is team fights is worst than litterally all of them 

She isn&#039;t as mobile as {{champion:67}} 

she can&#039;t fight tanks mid game like {{champion:96}} {{champion:67}} 

She can&#039;t defend herself like {{champion:67}} 

The only thing that trist can do better than the others is  push turrets, but {{champion:222}}  is arguably better at that than her 

Generalists aren&#039;t necassarily unhealthy to a role, Oriannia is a generalist mage that has been viable and rarely dominates the meta, but tristana shouldn&#039;t be one, or else she is going to have to be a weak champ, 

my suggestion is to push her more towards the seiging marksman since she&#039;s the only one who has an ability that directly interacts with turrets, making her bomb stacks go from 30% bonus per auto  to 50% on  turrets would give her a reason to be picked over the others, since she can now turn seige situations heavily in your teams favour
